metadata.author: ITS Music
metadata.description: Mental and physical health is very important to us. In all of ITS Music we encourage kindness, inclusivity, wellbeing, positivity and gratitude from an early age. With songs to help kids to get active and exercise, to songs about fruit and vegetables to encourage healthy eating, ITS Music provides songs to educate and entertain children of all ages.
